 For this investigation the chosen threshold was 25 (FFDI
\begin_inset script subscript

\begin_layout Plain Layout
>25
\end_layout

\end_inset

).
 Values above this threshold reflect days with very high to catastrophic
 bushfire danger.
 The data used for the analyses were seasonal values during spring (September-Oc
tober-November) and summer (December-January-February-March) of FFDI
\begin_inset script subscript

\begin_layout Plain Layout
cum
\end_layout

\end_inset

