After the bias-correction, the magnitude of FFDI results using reanalysis
 data is comparable to the computation with observations for the period
 1974-2010.
 During this period, the two types of data show that Victoria experienced
 a steep increase in fire danger.
 However, the FFDI computed with bias-corrected reanalysis data slightly
 over-estimates seasonal fire weather.
 On the other hand, FFDI
\begin_inset script subscript

